parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag warning indicator illumination can lead to a failure of the airbag system, which can result in serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning indicator light remains lit on the dashboard
warning messages appear on the iDrive screen
and the seat belt tensioner and passenger airbag may not function properly.
